-- BTG Pactual on 'conservative' side in risk allocation, CEO says
-- 
-- Wed May 07, 2014 12:49PM EDT
-- None



SAO PAULO, May 7 (Reuters) - Brazil's Grupo BTG Pactual SA <BBTG11.SA> Chief Executive Officer André Esteves said on Wednesday that Latin America's largest independent investment bank is right now "on the more conservative side" in terms of taking on new risk.   (Reporting by Guillermo Parra-Bernal)  ((guillermo.parra@thomsonreuters.com)(+55-11-5644-7714)(+55-119 -8346-7153)(Reuters Messaging: guillermo.parra.thomsonreuters.com@reuters.net))  Keywords: BTGPACTUAL RESULTS/RISK

